{"word":"ἀνάρμοστος","slug":"ἀνάρμοστος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνάρμοστος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἁρμόζω'><el>ἁρμόζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>unsuitable, incongruous, disproportionate</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—of sound, <i>out of tune</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-τως</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of persons, <i>impertinent, absurd</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>unfitted, unprepared</i>, <el>πρός τι</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}